text: Böblingen (Swabian: Landgraes Beblenga or Bebleng) is a rural district (Landkreis) in the middle of Baden-Württemberg, Germany. Neighboring districts are Calw, Esslingen, Enz, Ludwigsburg, Reutlingen, (district) Stuttgart, and Tübingen.
